\C[1]'s investigation skill activates! There was a
hidden door in the wall!

Hmm... If someone had learned \C[1]Investigation
Skill LV2\C[0], they might understand something...

I wonder if someone has \C[1]Investigation Skill
LV2\C[0]...

Oh my, well well... To think that it's the chief
of the succubus village herself...

So, you're the Demon King Mea, huh? Hmph, your
magical power isn't anything special.

\c[10]Demon King Mea\c[0] Kukuku... Dark, you can
only say that for now because I have you under my
control... There's nothing you can do against me.

\c[10]Demon King Mea\c[0], if you keep your
promise to teach me the release spell for this
Inma's Secret Treasure, I will guarantee Dark's
life...
As I thought, you had it...! You...

That person... Are you sure it's safe for them to
have the power of the secret treasure, Louisa?

It's not okay, but... I guess there's no other
choice...

\c[10]Demon King Mea\c[0], you truly are a
perceptive leader...

Louisa taught the release spell for the secret
treasure.
Alright, this should be enough! Release Dark!

\c[10]Demon King Mea\c[0]: Gyahahaha! Dark? I
wonder what you're talking about?

Wait, Louisa! This man isn't Dark...! It's another
corpse!

Mea-sama, the operation was a success... I have
obtained the spell for the secret treasure and
released its power...

Haah, you still haven't realized? I'm not Mea-
sama... Kukuku!

\c[10]Demon\c[0] Falling for such a cheap act,
both humans and lolimons are really stupid, huh?

Damn it... The power of the secret treasure... But
then, what about Dark?!

Louisa, this is a decoy! Dark was never captured
from the beginning!

Then, what about Aldo?! No way... but Aldo is
Dark's best friend, right? No way... but Aldo is
Dark's best friend, right?

Forget about that for now, let's defeat this guy
and retrieve the secret treasure first. Then, we
need to hurry back to the village!

Ngh...! Were you aiming to separate me from there
from the beginning?! How cunning...

\c[10]Demon\c[0], it seems you finally
understand... The power of this secret treasure
has already reached our master, the annihilator
Mea-sama... With overwhelming dominance, it will
seize control of the village...

Konoha, can I leave this small fry to you...? I'll
go back to the village first...!
Of course...! I'll go as fast as I can too...

\c[10]You may call me a weakling, but...? Even I
have my own... strength, you know... I won't let
myself fall behind a single magical girl, you
know?

Alright, for now let's retrieve the secret
treasure and hurry back to the village!
Hmmm? Are you a magical girl?
I will release the Demon King Mea... Daruku.

\c[10]Demon King Mea\c[0] Oh, the leader of the
succubi didn't come... That's a shame. However, I
can't just hand this man over to you. Not until I
hear the incantation of the sacred treasure...

I see, so the incantation is necessary to use the
sacred treasure. It's a shame, but I don't know
it.

\c[10]Demon King Mea\c[0] Kukuku... Well then,
listen to the incantation right now... Otherwise,
this man's life as a human will be forfeit...

Just kidding. We don't need any more theatrics.
That person over there isn't Daruku, and you're
not the Demon King Mea.

Actually, you wanted to lure Rudia here and attack
the village while she was distracted...

Demon Chi! Did you expose everything!? Aldo,
you've failed!
Eeek...! Th-this wasn't supposed to happen...!
Weren't you Daruku's best friend? Why on earth?

If I could attack the village... Mea-sama said she
would bring my dead sister back to life...

Finally, I can meet you...! My long-cherished wish
is coming true...!

Wake up, you're just being deceived. People don't
come back to life! You're just being used.

What are you saying...! Mea-sama wouldn't do such
a thing...! Are you trying to interfere... Magical
girl...!

\c[10]Demon\c[0]: Hmph, I'll leave it to Aldo
here... I'll go inform Lady Mea first... Make sure
to take care of things properly.

Leave it to me... Konoha-san, be prepared that I
won't come back alive from here.
◆◆◆◆◆◆「かかってきなさい」「軽くひねってあげるわ」◆◆◆◆◆◆

Now, let's go back to the village together and
talk about everything. Apologize.

You haven't become a bandit, right? You still have
a human heart, so it'll be okay.

We managed to avoid the worst-case scenario. The
treasure is still stolen, but let's go back to the
village and talk to Rudia.
By the way, where did Daruku end up after all?

Daruku was sent on an expedition for a quest in a
distant place. I think he will probably be back
soon.
Oh, good. Now, let's go back, Aldo.

I wouldn't underestimate me... I can rival Daruku,
you know...
